The 2nd Annual Los Angeles Online Film Critics Society Award Ceremony is set to award Brie Larson and John Cho Honorary Awards. The Los Angeles Online Film Critics Society is thrilled to announce that actress and filmmaker Brie Larson will be receiving their 2nd annual Trailblazer Award. In 2018, Jessica Chastain was the first recipient…
